metadata.description:
Small format mixedmedia artwork made on cardboard paper included in the phygital collection 'Parthenogenesis'. 

"You fell chasing the Moon. You rise through the Fracture."

♦️ This nft comes with the physical artwork

9.44" x 13.7" - 24 x 36 cm / Oil, Graphite Drawing Collage, Oil pastels, Paper on cardboard paper / Not signed / Framed / Multipanelled
